## [V0.0.4](https://github.com/Wasappli/WACoreDataSpotlight/releases/tag/0.0.4)

### Fixes
- Fixed an issue with cocoapods

## [V0.0.3](https://github.com/Wasappli/WACoreDataSpotlight/releases/tag/0.0.3)

### Fixes
- Use an expiration date builder block to define indexed items expiration date more precisely
- Added the `shouldIndexObjectBlock ` on mapping to allow not to index some objects if there are in a transient mode. For example: a booking not finalized.

## [V0.0.2](https://github.com/Wasappli/WACoreDataSpotlight/releases/tag/0.0.2)

### Fixes
- Fixed an infinited loop on `indexExistingObjects:`
- Added a new method to refresh an object indexing (after an image download for example) (`updateIndexingForObject:`)
- Update the index on `object context did save notification` instead of `objects did change`